Here is example of meta-layer with kernel module:
http://git.yoctoproject.org/cgit/cgit.cgi/poky/tree/meta-skeleton/recipes-kernel/hello-mod

If you want to use existing layers (meta-dht11, meta-diode_button_driver, meta-matrix_keypad),
you need to add this to bitbake-layers of your yocto project by command:
 $ bitbake-layers add-layer meta-agroinformer
Build bitbake-layer:
 $ bitbake agroinformer
